{"name":"Atlatl","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/javelin-tip-glowing-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A throwing board used to hurl darts or javelins with great force. The atlatl extends the thrower's arm, providing additional leverage and range.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> One-Handed, Ranged d8 (100/300), Reload (object interaction), Punch</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":100,"long":300,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","rel"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you score a mighty blow, before the target's next turn, the next attack against this target gains advantage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Blowgun","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/ammunition/arrow-head-war-pointed.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long tube used to shoot small darts by blowing air through it. Favored by those who value stealth and the ability to deliver poisons from a distance.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Light, One-Handed, Ranged d4 (25/100), Reload (free), Conceal, Hipshot</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":25,"long":100,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can load two darts and shoot two with the same attack roll at the same target or to two targets that are within 5 feet of one another. Each dart can deliver a poison or other payload, and when this weapon delivers poison, the enemy suffers disadvantage on the saving throw. Apply your ability modifier to damage on only one dart."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Portable Catapult","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact, deployable siege device capable of hurling heavy projectiles at enemies. Once set up, it can unleash devastating barrages of ammunition.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Affixed, Heavy, Ranged 2d8 (150/600), Reload (attack action), Knockback, Punch, Stagger, Trip</p>"},"price":{"value":175,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":20,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":8,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":150,"long":600,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","hvy","two","rel"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can load a full container of ammunition, e.g. 20 arrows or 50 needles, into the basket. As an action, you pick a point in range and release the basket. Each creature within a 20 ft radius cylinder, 60ft high centered on your point must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking a number of weapon damage dice equal to your proficiency bonus on a failed save, or half on a success."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Rope Dart","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/dart-feathered-yellow.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A weighted dart attached to a long rope, allowing the wielder to strike enemies at range and then retrieve the weapon. Its flexible nature enables a variety of combat techniques.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (20/50), Brace, Conceal, Entangle, Hipshot, Puncture</p>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":50,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can Brace as a bonus action and make a number of Brace attacks without using your reaction equal to your proficiency bonus before the start of your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Sling","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A simple but effective ranged weapon consisting of a pouch attached to two cords. Stones or lead bullets are whirled and released at high velocity. Can also be used as a melee weapon.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Ranged d8 (150/600), Reload (free), Conceal, Disarm</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":0.1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":150,"long":600,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"simpleR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On a mighty blow, the target must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or suffer disadvantage to attacks until the end of its next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Sling Staff","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A staff with a sling cup at one end, allowing both melee and ranged attacks. The staff's length also enables the Double Ended technique, striking with the opposite end.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Melee d6, Ranged d6 (150/600), Reload (free), Double Ended d8, Entangle</p>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":150,"long":600,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Your Double Ended attacks deal weapon damage plus your Strength modifier to your grappled target, and still automatically hit."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Sling Tube","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A rigid tube-shaped sling capable of launching various types of ammunition including bullets, bolts, and arrows. The tube's design allows for a wide spread of fire.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (60/180), Reload (object interaction), Conceal, Hipshot</p><p><em>Damage types: Bludgeoning, Piercing, or Slashing depending on ammunition used.</em></p>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":60,"long":180,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","two","rel"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can pack up to a full container of ammunition into the sling tube. As an action, you can launch all the ammunition in a 30 foot cone. Each creature in the cone must make a Dexterity saving throw. A target takes a number of weapon dice damage equal to your proficiency bonus on a failed save, or none on a success."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Wrist Shot","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/slings/sling-wrapped-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact wrist-mounted sling device, leaving the hands free while providing a concealed ranged attack option. Its surprising nature can catch enemies off guard.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (40/160), Disarm, Hipshot</p>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":160,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["amm","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Launch Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you score a mighty blow, your enemy loses its reaction until the start of its next turn. If you score a powerful blow, this effect applies, as well as all attacks against this enemy gain advantage until the end of your next turn. On a critical hit, these effects both apply."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Bite","type":"weapon","img":"icons/creatures/claws/mouth-teeth-long-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's jaws and teeth. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee, Entangle, Nimble, Wound</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can make a single bite attack as part of that action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Claw","type":"weapon","img":"icons/creatures/claws/claw-curved-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's claws. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee, Keen, Nimble, Wound</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you take the Attack action and hit with a melee attack, you can count that attack as a critical hit. Once you use this ability you cannot do so again until you finish a short rest."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Horns","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-hammer-destructive-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's horns or antlers. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Natural, Melee, Brace, Punch, Puncture, Sunder</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you move at least 20 feet in a straight line toward your target, you can make one melee attack with your horns as a bonus action. If this attack hits, your weapon damage dice is doubled."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Slam","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-hammer-destructive-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A powerful natural weapon attack using the creature's body mass — a fist, foot, or whole body impact. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Heavy, Natural, Melee, Brace, Disarm, Stagger</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you move at least 20ft straight toward an enemy and hit with a slam attack in the same turn, that enemy must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be knocked prone and you can make an additional slam attack as a bonus action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Tail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-hammer-destructive-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's tail. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Natural, Reach, Melee, Double Ended (one dice size smaller), Knockback, Trip</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As an action, you can attack all enemies within 5 feet of you."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Tentacle","type":"weapon","img":"icons/creatures/claws/tentacle-kraken-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's tentacle or appendage. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Light, Natural, Melee, Entangle, Trip</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When your target fails a saving throw against your Entangle attack, they become restrained and grappled."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Unarmed Strike","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using fists, feet, head, or any other part of the body. Damage is 1d4 + Strength modifier bludgeoning damage. RME properties apply on top of the base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee d4, Nimble</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"simpleM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can make an Unarmed strike as an off-hand attack even if your hands are occupied. You can spend a bonus action to shove or perform a Disarm attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Wings","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-hammer-destructive-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A natural weapon attack using the creature's wings to batter and buffet foes. Damage values are determined by the creature's stat block; RME properties apply on top of the creature's base attack.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Finesse, Natural, Melee, Deflect d6, Knockback, Trip</p>"},"price":{"value":0,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Natural Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As long as you do not already have disadvantage on your attack rolls, when you make your first attack on your turn, you can decide to attack defensively. Doing so gives you disadvantage on all weapon attack rolls during this turn, but attack rolls against you have disadvantage until your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Bladed Staff","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-flared-purple.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long staff with sharpened blades at both ends, allowing for swift and precise attacks. Its balanced design makes it equally effective at thrusting and sweeping strikes.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Reach, Melee 2d4, Double Ended d4, Balanced</p>"},"price":{"value":75,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you use the Double Ended property, you do not need to be within 5ft of your target."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Glaive","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/glaive-hooked-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long pole weapon with a single-edged blade on one end. The glaive's reach and versatility make it a fearsome weapon against multiple opponents, particularly effective against large creatures.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced, Brace</p>"},"price":{"value":20,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Against creatures of category size Large and larger, your damage is 3d6 instead of 2d6. Your Double Ended attack becomes 2d4."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Guisarme","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-hooked.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A pole weapon with a curved blade designed for hooking and tripping opponents. Its heavy head delivers devastating blows while its hook can tear mounted riders from their saddles.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee d12, Brace, Entangle, Trip</p>"},"price":{"value":20,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Your trip attacks impose disadvantage on saving throws made to resist them and if you succeed on a trip attack against a mounted enemy, it is automatically dismounted and lands prone in an unoccupied space of your choice within 5ft of its mount."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Lajatang","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-flared-purple.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A double-ended polearm with crescent-shaped blades at both ends. A weapon of rare elegance and deadly efficiency, demanding exceptional skill to master its spinning defensive and offensive techniques.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Heavy, Reach, Melee d10, Double Ended d10, Brace</p>"},"price":{"value":75,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":8,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On your turn, you can spend your reaction to enter a Defensive Stance, negating any flanking bonus or ability any enemy might have for flanking you or having the enemy's ally near you, such as pack tactics or sneak attack. You can use Double Ended twice on your turn, but your second attack must be against a different target than your first."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Naginata","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/glaive-hooked-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A Japanese-style curved blade mounted on a long pole. Light and swift, the naginata's keen edge and reach make it a weapon of grace and precision, capable of deflecting incoming attacks.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Finesse, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced, Keen</p>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can add your proficiency bonus to your Deflect roll."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Partisan","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-hooked.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy polearm with a broad blade and side prongs designed to catch and deflect enemy weapons. The partisan combines offensive reach with exceptional defensive capabilities.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Brace, Deflect, Riposte</p>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You have +1 weapon AC. When an enemy lands an attack on an ally within your range, you can use your reaction to force the enemy to reroll the attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Scythe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/scythe-curved-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A farming scythe adapted for use as a weapon of war, with the blade straightened or reset parallel to the shaft. Its sweeping cuts can carry through multiple targets.</p><p><strong>Basic:</strong> Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d4, Entangle, Keen, Puncture, Trip</p>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":8,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Polearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you reduce an enemy to 0 hit points with slashing damage, you can choose to apply the remaining damage to any other target within your range, instead of only adjacent targets."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
